    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/equality-monitoring-in-dsa-2010-11"/>
    <title>Equality monitoring in DSA 2010 to 2011</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>An analysis of staff diversity in DSA, for staff in post between 1st April 2010 and 31st March 2011.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="summary"&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An analysis of staff diversity, for staff in post between 1st April 2010 and 31st March 2011. The analysis looks at staff in post, cessations, grievances and discipline, training, sickness absence, performance markings and recruitment, and considers whether there were significant differences with respect to sex, race, disability, pay band, age, sexual orientation, religion and belief and working pattern.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
