    <title>DSA environmental sustainability policy statement</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>DSA acknowledges that it has a responsibility to recognise and manage the impact that its activities have on the environment.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Driving Standards Agency (&lt;abbr title="Driving Standards Agency"&gt;DSA&lt;/abbr&gt;) acknowledges that it has a responsibility to recognise the impact that its activities have on the environment and to mange those impacts so that they can be reduced or removed. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;abbr title="Driving Standards Agency"&gt;DSA&lt;/abbr&gt;’s environmental policy statement outlines its aims and objectives by showing how it has integrated this into the organisation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
